Body:
I cannot get the graphs and statistics of collect view example. I have run the simulation for many minutes, but when I go to tools and select collect view the nodes portion in the next window is empty and I have also selected start collect and send commands to nodes but no luck nothing shows up on the graphs :

"
did you solve this problem? i still have this problem!

The answer is that the devices do not send the relevant parameters. If you have made the necessary adjustments, you can see the battery and other operations of the devices. Samples of sink.c and sender.c will help your work. At first I had worked hard on me, but later I managed to solve this problem with the related settings.
